<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Cochrane Modern RE — Flip Atlas v{{ version }}</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta property="og:title" content="Cochrane Modern RE — Flip Atlas">
<meta property="og:description" content="Modern random-effects methods vs RevMan defaults across {{ n_mas }} Cochrane pairwise meta-analyses.">
<style>
  body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
         max-width: 1100px; margin: 2em auto; padding: 0 1em; color: #222;
         line-height: 1.5; }
  h1 { border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: .3em; }
  h2 { margin-top: 1.8em; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: .2em; }
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 1em 0; font-size: 0.92em; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 4px 8px; text-align: right; }
  th { background: #eee; }
  td:first-child, td:nth-child(2), td:nth-child(3),
  th:first-child, th:nth-child(2), th:nth-child(3) { text-align: left; }
  .summary { background: #f6f6f6; padding: 1em 1.2em; border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
             margin: 1em 0; }
  .summary p { margin: .4em 0; }
  .headline { font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: bold; color: #0066cc; }
  .sparse td { color: #888; font-style: italic; }
  footer { margin-top: 3em; padding-top: 1em; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
           color: #666; font-size: 0.9em; }
  code { background: #f6f6f6; padding: 1px 4px; border-radius: 3px;
         font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Cochrane Modern RE — Flip Atlas <small>v{{ version }}</small></h1>

<div class="summary">
  <p><strong>Corpus:</strong> {{ n_mas }} pairwise meta-analyses across {{ n_reviews }} Cochrane systematic reviews (Pairwise70).</p>
  <p><strong>Methods compared:</strong> DL (baseline), REML_only, REML+HKSJ+PI, <code>bayesmeta</code> half-normal.</p>
  <p><strong>Headline significance-flip rate (DL → REML+HKSJ+PI):</strong>
     <span class="headline">{{ "%.1f"|format(headline_rate * 100) }}%</span>
     <small>({{ comparator_description }})</small>
  </p>
</div>

<h2>Tier 1 — Significance flips by stratum</h2>
<p><em>CI excludes null under baseline but includes null under comparator (or vice versa).</em></p>
{{ tier1_table|safe }}

<h2>Tier 2 — Direction flips by stratum</h2>
<p><em>Sign of pooled point estimate changes (protective → harmful or vice versa).</em></p>
{{ tier2_table|safe }}

<h2>Tier 3 — Clinically-important flips (MID-available subset)</h2>
<p><em>|Δ pooled effect| exceeds the MID for that outcome. Reported only on the MID-available subset; NA for outcomes not in the MID lookup table.</em></p>
{{ tier3_table|safe }}

<footer>
  <p>Generated {{ generated_at }} UTC. Source: <a href="https://github.com/mahmood726-cyber/cochrane-modern-re">cochrane-modern-re</a>. Target journal: Research Synthesis Methods.</p>
  <p>Related: <a href="https://github.com/mahmood726-cyber/repro-floor-atlas">repro-floor-atlas</a> (reproduction-floor primitive).</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
